                                <div class="speaker speaker-meta section">
                                    <div class="col span_2_of_3 speaker-bio">
                                        <p>Nikita Singh is the author of two books- Love @ Facebook and Accidentally in Love. Both of which were written in under two weeks, and went on to become super-hits. Through her literary endeavours, Nikita has managed to reconcile the oxymoron in ‘intelligent chick-lit’.</p>

<p>In Nikita’s Utopia, she would be the author of fantasy fiction, and let her imagination run wild with vampires and witches.</p>

<p>A self-confessed foodie on her Twitter profile, her tweets also reveal that she is a die-hard romantic.</p>

